title: Avaya Devices: Passport Modules
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/avaya
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the operational status of passport modules on Avaya devices.

 Depending on the reported state the service goes {OK}, {WARN}, {CRIT} or {UNKNOWN}.

 Per default the service is

 - {OK} for "up", "testing", "dormant"

 - {CRIT} for "down"

 - {UNKNOWN} for "unknown"

 The outcome of the states is configureable.

 The check uses the RAPID-CITY-MIB.

item:
 The index of the card.

inventory:
 One service is created for each installed card.
